Game class
----------

This event operates on an instance of the [game class](Game_class "Game class") type {{{gameclass}}}

Description
-----------

Stops an ongoing effect.

Usage
-----

*void* stopEffect( *string* **effectName** )

Parameters
----------

-   [effectName] - Name of effect to stop.

Examples
--------

    $my_entity.stopEffect( "fire64" );

Notes
-----

This script event does not return any values. See the [PlayEffect](PlayEffect_%28script_event%29 "PlayEffect (script event)") event.


